item.title: By: Brenna
item.dc:creator: Brenna
item.description:
I love my Mr. Wiggles. Matter of fact we just soloed ZG yesterday. He is an amazing tank and can hold aggro like no other. Even after proving himself time and time again my guildies see him for one thing and one thing only too, I'm afraid. Dinner!
MR. WIGGLES FTW!

item.title: By: winter
item.dc:creator: winter
item.description:
I took Mr. Wiggles with me to go kill Onyxia, but at the end of the battle, he was no where to be see.
I later saw some guild mate chowing down on BBQ pork spare ribs. I fear for my little guy....
